{"tid":939432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民眾托木送中國駐加使館        代加國政府致歉","createTime":"2018-12-13T06:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T09:57:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0e781afb35a0afd9b7f3ed7f940a74944bc0d9b3","tid":939432,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181213/large/1544678262_578d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181213%2Flarge%2F1544678262_578d.jpg&h=131c8bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為太子女兼副董事長孟晚舟被加拿大當局拘押，雖然已獲准保釋，惟事件不斷發酵，更讓中加兩國緊張。中國駐加拿大使館公佈消息，指當地時間12月12日，一名加拿大市民到中國駐加使館，送上一段他親手砍伐的雲杉木。<br />\n<br />\n該名加拿大市民表示，自己是一名伐木工人，對加方日前在溫哥華拘押孟晚舟感到憤慨。有說該塊雲杉木打橫看，有點似象徵加拿大的「北極熊」，希望以此表達其對中國人民的友好感情。作為一個加拿大人，代加政府的錯誤行為向中國人民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n公告又提及，連日來，許多加拿大普通民眾不斷向中國駐加使館致電、發電郵或在網上發帖，批評加方應美方要求拘押中國公民，呼籲加拿大政府立即釋放孟晚舟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181213/59024990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181213%2F59024990&d=KnvXPE3nScOl%2BNY7DWqCyjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8323cf5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181213%2F59024990&h=1c9d88f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181213/59024990</a>"},{"pid":"acf036760df8bf1afec9f27329cf95e4db140f49","tid":939432,"uid":14918,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"民<span style=\"color: red;\">眾</span>???"},{"pid":"9037fc9b27480699be27a6c9c8f61eb1d4b427f6","tid":939432,"uid":63154,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T06:36:39.000Z","msg":"Fake news 味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd7683f6d122f7cba0e